    <p>3</p>
    <p>Cu­ri­ous about things that go bump in the night? The Creepy Tales of Sin­ga­pore tour takes you to a ceme­tery and World War II sites. Or­gan­ised by Ori­en­tal Travel and Tours, par­tic­i­pants will be armed with can­dles and equip­ment used to de­tect para­nor­mal ac­tiv­ity.</p>
    <p>$315 for a group of five, down from $750. From Aug 19 to Sept 16, to mark the Hun­gry Ghost Fes­ti­val. Use the promo code “ST30” when book­ing on­line. Other dis­counts may ap­ply out­side of these dates.</p>
    <p>www.ori­en­tal.tours</p>
    <p>Price: Info:</p>

